To install database using ant you must have ant already installed.
If you do not then visit http://ant.apache.org/.

change into install/database/scripts and execute the following command

ant -buildfile DBLoader.xml

To install database using Groovy you must have Groovy already installed.
If you do not then visit http://groovy.codehaus.org/.

change into install/database/scripts and execute the following command

groovy DBLoader.groovy